{"tid":1050650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍設1.5萬人太空部隊　規模最小","createTime":"2019-03-07T04:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T06:15:59.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a88c750802745b71b3e6233e50115802592a8bce","tid":1050650,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"美軍設1.5萬人太空部隊　規模最小<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190303/20624855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F20624855&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=2eab5efe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F20624855&h=555f55a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190303/20624855</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部前日公佈太空部隊計劃書，顯示政府將於未來五年增設太空部隊，成為美軍第六個軍種，但成員只有1.5萬名，是屬眾多軍種中規模最小的一個。計劃已於上周三上呈國會，要求在現時太空軍事活動開支外再額外撥款20億美元（156億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>被斥架床叠屋</strong><br />\n<br />\n太空部隊將是自1947年空軍獨立後首個新軍種，將設於空軍架構之下，由一名四星上將出任參謀長，向空軍部長威爾遜負責。部隊擬於明年成立，起初只有200人，但計劃書未有披露會否自設軍營作招募，或會否有自行設計的軍服。而並非所有太空任務均由太空部隊負責，如導彈防禦局、太空總署、國家偵察局則不納入太空部隊。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普積極推動國防部建設與其他軍種同級但獨立的太空部隊。前國防部長馬蒂斯認為此舉「架床叠屋」增加軍費開支。外界亦質疑另立太空部隊的需要，指要執行太空任務只需極少數人。國防部則指另立軍種可在軍隊內加強太空議題的聲音，並創建獨特的太空文化和專業。署理國防部長夏納翰形容這是歷史時刻，指美國可於在「複雜的領域上競爭和勝出」，又讚揚特朗普的「雄才偉略」。目前規模最小的軍種為海岸警衞隊，現役成員約4萬人，架構上屬國土安全部。第二最小的為海軍陸戰隊，約18.6萬人。最大的是陸軍，成員人數達48.75萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"5aec1d9b5f48dd4d5acd1c4bd64eb3bd436260e6","tid":1050650,"uid":63909,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5efx8ck.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5efx8ck.png&h=044f464c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf69c8080785d45d8130e6fe82698d6eb891280a","tid":1050650,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外界亦質疑另立太空部隊的需要，指要執行太空任務只需極少數人。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n月球同火星喎"},{"pid":"d8e67249b3fd637fbc6d24936d964b0e2be0329a","tid":1050650,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"現代軍隊，後勤、文職真係好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a237a2f9ecaa708ab6d1f7830f87e81e0f38a1f3","tid":1050650,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e67249b3fd637fbc6d24936d964b0e2be0329a","tid":1050650,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"現代軍隊，後勤、文職真係好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:35:44.000Z","msg":"武器研發<br />\n太空武器同地表都唔同啦"},{"pid":"43cd67c0ec73876bdeae56884706caf19c35fccc","tid":1050650,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"前國防部長馬蒂斯認為此舉「架床叠屋」增加軍費開支。<br />\n<br />\n咪扮野外星人d料你會唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710fcaf396cf80b1301a84ccbd7c0cbfefecd6ab","tid":1050650,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aec1d9b5f48dd4d5acd1c4bd64eb3bd436260e6","tid":1050650,"uid":63909,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5efx8ck.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5efx8ck.png&h=044f464c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fc27b6fadbff36a4ddcf063582157321766a79","tid":1050650,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43cd67c0ec73876bdeae56884706caf19c35fccc","tid":1050650,"uid":103230,"like":10,"d